      "description": "The page's stylesheets contain no rules that adapt to the user's `prefers-reduced-motion` OS setting. Users with vestibular disorders who request reduced motion will still see every animation at full amplitude.",
      "element": {
        "selector": "stylesheet",
        "html_snippet": "",
