      "description": "The page has no styles scoped to `forced-colors: active`. In Windows High Contrast mode (and macOS/iOS increased contrast) the browser overrides colors using system palette; author styles often lose semantic distinctions (e.g. disabled vs. active buttons become identical).",
      "element": {
