      "fix_suggestion": "Test the page with Windows High Contrast or Chrome's `Emulate CSS media feature forced-colors` devtool. Add `@media (forced-colors: active)` rules that use system colors (`CanvasText`, `Highlight`, `ButtonText`, etc.) or `forced-color-adjust: none` where custom colors are semantically required."
